data.description: HUGE Incentives! $7,000. Seller Concession to Buyer, Super Low VA loan is Assumable! Home highlights: Solar Panels, water softener, Reverse Osmosis, ENVIROMAX HEPA Filter & extended patio with Pergola. Plus, no direct back neighbor set this gem of a home apart from the rest. Step inside this inviting home and be greeted by an open floor plan designed for comfort and functionality, adorned with luxury vinyl planking floors that ensures low maintenance. The kitchen and living room flow creates an inviting space ideal for seamless entertaining. A spacious living area upstairs provides versatile possibilities, whether you envision a play area, game room, or additional living space to suit your needs. The four well-proportioned rooms are thoughtfully located on the upper level, ensuring ample privacy and personal space. The backyard is a true retreat, featuring a covered patio to unwind and relax. With a greenbelt backdrop, you'll relish the privacy and natural beauty surrounding your home. This residence embodies the perfect blend of peaceful living and modern convenience. Immerse yourself in the charm and allure of West San Antonio, and make this inviting home your sanctuary. Schedule a showing today and imagine the possibilities of making this delightful house your forever home. Conveniently located near Loop 1604, Hwy 90 & 211 puts you minutes from Lackland AFB, Downtown SA, and lots of shopping & restaurants. Act now & you can be Home for The Holiday's!
